skins.shipDescription: Fletcher-class destroyer ¨C Bush, Hull Number DD-529.
skins.selfIntroduction: I'm the Fletcher-class destroyer Bush. Like my sisters, I fought in the Pacific Ocean and took on tons of missions! ... Planes? I-I don't wanna talk about those scary things!
skins.acquisition: I'm Bush, from the Fletcher class! I'll be staying here from now on!
skins.login: Umm... What are we doing today, again?
skins.details: What is it? Do you want something from me?
skins.secretaryIdle1: If I stay out of sight, the Commander probably won't notice I'm neglecting my work...
skins.secretaryIdle2: Uughh... Following a schedule is so boooring! I say we do stuff when we see it needs doing! ... What? That's not gonna fly?
skins.secretaryIdle3: I've got a bunch of sisters, both younger and older than me! I forget their names all the time, though...
skins.secretarySpecialTouch: It's not okay to touch me like that!
